Tensaku
=======

Tensaku is a fork of Satty, a modern screenshot annotation tool for Linux.

    Upstream project:  Satty
    Original author:   Matthias Gabriel <gabm+aur@mailbox.org>
    Upstream source:   https://github.com/Satty-org/Satty

All source files inherited from Satty were created by Matthias Gabriel
and the Satty contributors. The fork point is git commit
d19a403d6fd2854eaacd277998bf6c5cba85f7a5; per-file and per-line
authorship for inherited files is preserved in this repository's git
history (see `git log` / `git blame`). Files and modifications added
after that commit are contributed by the Tensaku authors.

